Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93156,95241}It came, it came! My dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:36.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95241,96826}- Look!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96826,98786}Hurry up ​​and adjust the clock time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98786,100538}What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100538,102582}It's 2:55!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102582,103583}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:47.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103583,107253}This dog is always here at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108421,110840}My home clock stopped working!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110840,113217}This is the best way to adjust the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:54.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113217,114052}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124228,125021}Hey, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125647,127190}Are you going today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127190,128024}Is it hard work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129942,131319}I understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132362,134656}You don't understand what I'm saying to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165895,168564}How come you don't know the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169065,170566}Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172276,174821}No, I really don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174821,176864}I'm tired…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176864,179283}I said the answer during the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179283,181369}You didn't payed attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182078,183746}Don't stick out your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192797,194173}I finished the lesson today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194173,195925}I will leave you to find the answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196259,197427}John Carraclogh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197427,198344}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198344,200012}You, give me the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:21.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200805,201556}Eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201764,202807}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203099,205727}… three hundred and forty…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205727,207019}… No, twenty…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207019,208438}Sorry, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208688,209605}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209605,210773}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:33.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211399,213776}I'm still standing, can I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214026,215069}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215069,216195}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216195,217697}Isn't it obvious that you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218281,220700}What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231252,233004}Oh my God, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233004,235298}How long will we do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235298,236507}Oh really…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238092,240386}Today he was very angry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240386,242096}But Sandy made him even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242096,244974}You don't had to act provocatively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244974,248102}Besides the teacher's anger\Nincreased more when she said:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248102,251522}"I'm still standing, can I sit?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251522,254400}I wish you were as indifferent as she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254400,255526}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257945,260156}I know I'm a totally indifferent girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260156,261741}I apologize for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261741,264285}Sandy, what happened to you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264285,268456}I envy you for your character, Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268456,271834}It's because of me, although I imagined\Nprolonging the time of your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:37.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272460,277006}I worked hard to think about answering longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277298,278883}But this…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:43.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278883,283679}You mean the teacher\Nis very angry because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283679,285556}You, too, John…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285556,287433}Just consider me a troublesome girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297485,298069}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298069,299612}Hello, Lassie! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299612,301656}We were late because of Sandy's behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301656,303991}Don't say anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316379,318881}You waited John for a long time, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319382,320424}You are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321509,324136}Come on, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:36.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332937,336649}I expected. It's better to apologize, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336649,337441}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337441,340987}I have a lot of work in the store\Nso I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341696,344115}Sandy is just as well at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344115,345616}The study is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346492,347869}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347869,349287}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349287,351163}If you apologize, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:56.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351163,356252}Today, I have to take the goods\Nfrom the store to Morton's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356252,357753}Hi Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359714,362633}Well, Colin left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378983,381777}Lassie, I can't play with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381777,383571}Because I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387742,388534}Wel…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389702,391287}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391287,392079}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392079,395166}I didn't know that such words\Nwould anger Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396000,397710}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:43.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398711,403257}But when Sandy comes tomorrow\Nshe'll forget everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403257,404926}Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404926,405801}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405801,408304}Lassie doesn't need food today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408304,409722}Ah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409722,411432}What is the matter? What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411432,415603}You can't forget the precious Lassie's meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415603,417897}Thank you, Mr. Nelson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417897,421233}You can come here for the weekend as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421233,423527}Well, I'll tell my father that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423527,425196}Yes that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425196,427782}Today you were a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427782,430368}Have you been punished\Nbecause you haven't studied well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430368,431619}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431619,433829}It's a really good dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433829,434622}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435039,437249}We have talked about it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437249,440294}We have never seen a good dog like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440294,442296}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442296,444590}Every morning it follows me annoyingly…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444590,446509}It's as I said about it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446509,450680}It's persistent even if the winds\Nof Yorkshire are very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450680,451847}It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:37.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451847,457395}Right! It's a good dog and the best in Yorkshire!\NEven if the owner leaves it, it can live the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457395,458896}As I expected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469407,471701}"Even if the owner leaves it,\Nit can live the best."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471701,473536}It won't be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479000,480876}Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481168,483587}You dig again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483587,485548}What exactly do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486048,488259}You can't get inside looking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488259,490886}If you enter, the room will be stained with mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491554,493305}You are useless…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494724,495891}Hey, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496517,498978}You do this every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498978,500104}Well, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501731,503899}In fact you are annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504316,506402}Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507028,508696}He seems angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508696,510031}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510031,513075}Maybe he's trying to act\Nlike a little mature person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513075,516203}John! I don't know what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516203,518539}but stop bothering Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518539,520833}It's not like I'm bothering it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520833,523836}Lassie is the one who causes me discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524045,525046}Hm…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525046,526088}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526464,530259}I told it to always stay at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530259,532636}but it follows me every morning to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532636,535723}Even when I go home\Nit's waiting in front of the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535723,536307}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536307,537516}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538100,541145}This water is not to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541479,544273}And now I'm going to the second floor, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566754,568047}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568047,570132}Don't do this…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570132,571842}You are no longer a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571842,573719}Don't sneak in here that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575554,576680}With such a face…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576680,579725}You don't want to be seen this way\Nby Mr. Nelson the butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580267,582394}Somehow you look terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582394,584647}It's best to comb your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594365,597118}You, do you have fleas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597118,599537}Do you have such things for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599537,601497}Where did you get it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606210,607461}Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614135,616011}I said don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616011,617888}I have to go to school alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617888,620141}You can go and play by yourself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624019,625479}I'm sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625479,627815}Even though you have walked\Nall this distance for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627815,630651}However, it's inevitable\Nas long as he is still feverish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:36.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631652,636073}Please, when Colin gets better,\Nlet him go back to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636073,637700}Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637700,639618}He will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639618,641245}- Goodbye, Uncle!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652423,655050}That is why I told you\Nnot to follow me like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655050,657136}Let me walk more freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657636,658637}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676322,679533}Well… Go now! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679533,680659}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702806,705935}Oh Lassie, you also came today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706310,708938}I have enough food too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:52.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708938,712942}You always help me, take care of the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714109,715945}You are good!
Comment: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:02.49,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:722493,722493}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741220,744723}Besides Colin, Sandy is also absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745766,748644}This way I can't apologize to her\Nfor what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795607,798777}Oh! I was about to forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799069,801864}You are really useful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801864,805909}You learned many things\Njust by staying with Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805909,808120}Now the farm is big and it needs you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808120,809288}isn't it, Bingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810581,811749}And now Lassie,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811749,814043}what time did you return?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814043,815336}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815336,817254}This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817254,818255}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911306,912891}Well, it's its share of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913809,914852}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914852,916061}But, Uncle…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:19.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916061,919314}Lassie doesn't persevere even\Nif the winds of Yorkshire are very cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919314,920649}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920649,923861}I was the one who took care of it\Nall the time and taught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923861,926405}Lassie can't do anything without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926780,928282}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928282,930409}You are also a great boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931326,932369}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932369,934997}I'm glad you told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934997,936290}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941086,943755}Have we made any mistake about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943755,945799}No, I don't know…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980459,981919}Don't try in your usual way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996308,997601}Now let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999478,1001855}What will we play today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003857,1006109}I remembered, there is an abandoned mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006109,1008237}Do you want to look for treasures together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:11.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026838,1031093}I haven't seen this abandoned mine\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032177,1034721}The interior is very dark and terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035681,1037933}I wonder if you will follow me, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037933,1040727}I don't think this area is\Nas cowardly as you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041478,1042771}Well, I'll go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056535,1057411}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057411,1059454}Lassie, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091278,1093071}When I was little I was playing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093071,1094698}It will be difficult for Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102748,1103624}Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:32.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108337,1112758}How can Lassie chase me this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122392,1123644}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123644,1125812}Hey! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129274,1131526}Wait for me, I will ask for help now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131526,1132486}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144915,1146333}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147334,1149419}I think that was my fault…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150379,1151338}I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:17.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152923,1157844}Somehow I feel that this vast sky\Nis much farther than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158762,1160097}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160097,1162140}Wouldn't anyone come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162849,1164267}Tell me, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165268,1167312}Lassie, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167312,1168730}Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171149,1172776}That's great…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172776,1175612}I thought you were hurt or died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:40.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177489,1180325}I'm really sorry, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180325,1182744}I don't know why but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182744,1186373}…all people are very grateful to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187082,1189292}In fact I'm very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189292,1191128}but at the same time I'm not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:54.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191878,1194131}I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195465,1197384}I can't understand Sandy's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197801,1200595}Because of this I'm angry with you,\Nand I don't want to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200595,1204683}I felt nervous and threw everything on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204683,1207894}You are my most important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210063,1211773}I'm sorry, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213400,1215277}I want to see your face again…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216403,1219906}Lassie, I'd do anything for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223744,1225370}Lassie, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249311,1251104}What's up, Bingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254357,1256234}What? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260280,1261281}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261281,1262574}From here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:03.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262949,1263909}Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264534,1267245}What? John, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267245,1269873}Wait, I will help you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275587,1276755}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277172,1278548}Eat…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278548,1281009}…as an apology for that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281009,1284387}Sandy, you're absent today also…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284387,1286848}Apology? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286848,1288767}As I expected…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289017,1290227}By the way, John,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290227,1292479}I took a vacation because\Nof a pain in my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292479,1295649}Why do you got me something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295649,1297442}Can't you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297442,1299778}I thought you had a fever like Colin!
